data.title: Alexandra Reeve Givens
data.meta_description: Alexandra Reeve Givens. Additional Crew: Das Fenster zum Hof. Alexandra Reeve Givens was born in December 1983 in London, England, UK. She is known for Das Fenster zum Hof (1998). She has been married to Garren Givens since 6 September 2008. They have one child.
data.text:
She and her older brother, Matthew Reeve, are the children of the late Superman actor Christopher Reeve and Gae Exton.

Gave birth to her 1st child at age 31, a son named Christopher Russel Reeve Givens on June 13, 2015 in Washington, D.C. weighed in at 8 lbs., 3 oz. He was named after his grandfathers on each side. Child's father is her husband, Garren Givens.
